# Managed / CNG workflow: ios/ and android/ are LOCAL PREBUILD ARTIFACTS (gitignored,
# 0 tracked files). The source of truth for native config is app.json + its config plugins.
# .easignore overrides .gitignore for the EAS upload archive, so without these lines EAS
# would upload the stale local prebuild and skip prebuild — shipping an outdated Info.plist
# instead of app.json's config. Exclude them so EAS regenerates native config from app.json.
ios/
android/

# Design references & QA artifacts — keep in the repo, never ship in the build.
docs/
qa/

# Local source nebula artwork (gitignored, unreferenced at runtime — the live nebula
# renderer is procedural SVG). .easignore overrides .gitignore for the EAS archive, so
# without this line these ~19 MB of untracked PNGs would still upload/embed. Exclude them.
assets/nebula-art/
